<br>
ursh has it right he been pvping lots longer than i have, i can kill just about any class in a duel, except shaman with sow boots and fef undispellable dots. <br>
<br>
casual pvp for a mage in anything but a darky zone on VZ jsut simply does not happen, rarely when i see a light from an opposing guild in a zone that i dont put up a pet, cast expediance and make sure i am fully buffed if i am expecting pvp.<br>
<br>
resists are simply too high for earth pet to be effective, air does not stun, fire is a literal joke, water is the only choice cause when  running in circles from a melee your pet can land BS's. the  nuke lands sometimes and is funny to watch too =)<br>
<br>
most melees have enough HP's and resists to just tank my pet, even with a ds on, and kill it then go after me. but most melees also dont know about  chain casting pets =)<br>
<br>
leviatation and jboots are a must. skill as a mage in pvp is really tested, i feel sorry for wizards who  can only nuke and not rely  on pets, when a_random_epicified_monkwitht-staff_01 finds you it  tends to help  to run<br>
<br>
my observation  lvl 1-57 so far on a pvp server =)<br>
